node.text:
Nearly 60 years ago, #Kleinfeld bride Karen found her wedding dress at our former Bay Ridge location. 👰‍♀️ To celebrate her 59th wedding anniversary, Karen dusted off her dress (which still fit her like a glove🧤) for a special day with the love of her life, Gary ‼️

“My grandparents got to relive their wedding day all over again! They did a first look and it brought tears to all of our eyes,” says photographer @NikkiRyanPhotography. 🥺💕“They cut their cake, made a toast, and even did their first dance. Their love is one of a kind and still look at each other and kiss the way they did on their wedding day.” 💍  Swipe for a look at the couple in 1962 vs 2021! Tag the Gary to your Karen in the comments below!👇 l 📸 @mccallryan
